<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.censusindia.gov.in/Census_Data_2001/Census_Data_Online/Language/Statement1.htm" class="external text" rel="nofollow">Census of India 2001</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4">^</a></b> <a href="https://rni.nic.in/display_language.asp" class="external free" rel="nofollow">https://rni.nic.in/display_language.asp</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
